# SimpleOS — Microkernel-based Desktop Operating System
#
# Architecture:
#   Layer 0: Boot (Limine, BSD-2-Clause)
#   Layer 1: Kernel (scheduler, VMM, IPC, capabilities)
#   Layer 2: Services (init, VFS/FAT32, net, drivers)
#   Layer 3: Compositor (framebuffer + window manager)
#   Layer 4: Desktop Apps (terminal, file manager, editor)
#   Layer 5: LLM Integration (MCP OS server + widget DSL)
#
# Target: x86_64 (QEMU), RISC-V 64 (later)
# Security: Capability-based (Capsicum + OpenBSD inspired)

use os.kernel
use os.services
use os.drivers
use os.compositor
use os.desktop
use os.apps
